name: Elon Musk Facial Expression
description: Inking of Elon Musk doing a Facial Expression. Inked using a japanese Pentel Pocket Brush on a special and unique paper made by the Santiago de Chile Stock Exchange for the 2013 Cultural Heritage Day of Chile. The size of the piece is 21cm (8.2in) in lenght and 16,5cm (6.5in) in width.  This piece is both digital and physical as I will send the original art piece to the buyer together with a certificate issued by the Chilean National Museum of Fine Arts. Final note: This art piece will be shipped worldwide and the shipping cost is included in its price.
